{"tid":2142546,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不出去的禮拜天 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:04:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15057603e6aa5e4a21bf1bc82b2acf2fe83f57c5","tid":2142546,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/UHKWP3TEK5HGXPBN6KH5GV5ZRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FUHKWP3TEK5HGXPBN6KH5GV5ZRM%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOllQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=a0e0f1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FUHKWP3TEK5HGXPBN6KH5GV5ZRM%2F&h=cfb5f927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/UHKWP3TEK5HGXPBN6KH5GV5ZRM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不出去的禮拜天 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DA9i0C7TYcapCtEYea1M-7LJGL4=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WLTOY5UE4RGM5NQDTO3AN6UTRU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDA9i0C7TYcapCtEYea1M-7LJGL4%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWLTOY5UE4RGM5NQDTO3AN6UTRU.JPG&h=536e3009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實每個人的人生都是一種自我選擇，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有時我們不禁為已逝去的人惋惜，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在這一個不出去的星期天，選擇了什麼也不做，不伏案、不上街市、不下廚、不等待，總算有一個完全屬於自己的假日，可以奢侈的揮霍着光陰，從清晨數看着日影推移，明或暗的光影中黃昏已過，黑夜降臨，不知多少個星期天過去，若不是這次日益嚴峻的疫情，人人自危下的自保，應該一早到街市；也曾有過&mdash;&mdash;一個上午三個街市採購配料的例子。如今足不出戶閒了下來，為自己曾有過的瞎忙失笑。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼總要等到事過情遷後才來緬懷昔日？如今，人不來訪、你不去探人，比鄰若天涯王不見王的時刻才深深感覺到原以為尋常的昔日竟不可得，忽忽歲已晚，覺來不可追。"},{"pid":"4c0bbc3b9168698ff027e0fced8c6d6334c3bee3","tid":2142546,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"【飛雲】影一張相等於7000蚊嘅時代來臨了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9351c1a3e53e7e998a19deac5ed1a9ebb8210104","tid":2142546,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"仆街睇咗麗"}]}